{"file_name": "Arts_multipage.pdf", "file_type": "pdf", "confidence": 0.78, "time_taken": 1.38, "memory_mb": 3.75, "units": [{"index": 1, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.79, "text": {"text": "ANANYA MEHRA\nVisual Artist / Creative Professional\nMumbai, India | ananya.mehra@email.com | +91-9XXXXXXXXX\nPROFESSIONAL SUMMARY\nVisual Artist with 10+ years of experience in fine arts, mixed media, illustration, and contemporary visual practices.\nStrong background in concept development, visual storytelling, and exhibition curation. Experienced in\ncollaborating with galleries, cultural institutions, and interdisciplinary teams to deliver compelling artistic outcomes.\nARTISTIC SKILLS & MEDIUMS\n(cid:127) Fine Arts: Acrylic, Oil, Watercolor\n(cid:127) Mixed Media & Installation Art\n(cid:127) Illustration & Concept Art\n(cid:127) Digital Art: Photoshop, Procreate\n(cid:127) Visual Storytelling & Composition\n(cid:127) Exhibition Design & Curation\nPROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE\nIndependent Visual Artist (2016 \u2013 Present)\n(cid:127) Created original artworks for solo and group exhibitions at national and international galleries.\n(cid:127) Developed thematic series exploring identity, culture, and urban life.\n(cid:127) Collaborated with curators and cultural organizations for site-specific installations and public art projects.\n(cid:127) Managed the full creative lifecycle from ideation to final presentation.", "tables": []}}, {"index": 2, "method": "structured", "confidence": 0.76, "text": {"text": "Illustrator & Art Educator (2012 \u2013 2016)\n(cid:127) Delivered commissioned illustrations for editorial, branding, and publishing projects.\n(cid:127) Conducted art workshops and training programs for students and emerging artists.\n(cid:127) Mentored junior artists on technique, portfolio development, and conceptual thinking.\nEXHIBITIONS & PROJECTS\n(cid:127) Solo Exhibition \u2013 \u201cUrban Narratives\u201d, Mumbai Art Gallery\n(cid:127) Group Exhibition \u2013 National Contemporary Art Show, Delhi\n(cid:127) Public Art Installation \u2013 City Cultural Festival, Mumbai\nEDUCATION\n(cid:127) Bachelor of Fine Arts (BFA) \u2013 Sir J.J. School of Art, Mumbai\nAWARDS & RECOGNITION\n(cid:127) Emerging Artist Award \u2013 State Art Council\n(cid:127) Featured Artist \u2013 National Art Magazine\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION\n(cid:127) Strong visual communication and presentation skills\n(cid:127) Experience working with multidisciplinary creative teams\n(cid:127) Passionate about cultural storytelling and contemporary art practices", "tables": []}}], "error": null, "embedding": [0.04996322840452194, -0.03977660462260246, -0.002320649800822139, -0.03181219846010208, 0.0572635680437088, 0.0062333024106919765, 0.037855882197618484, 0.02823098748922348, -0.026932384818792343, -0.05228343978524208, -0.0071273609064519405, -0.017383072525262833, -0.017315490171313286, 0.030767183750867844, 0.05902480334043503, 0.04542149230837822, 0.03702719509601593, 0.0009359074174426496, 0.020072417333722115, -0.007315294351428747, -0.003392197657376528, -0.011450894176959991, -0.00705073494464159, 0.06821398437023163, 0.004698112141340971, -0.03700621426105499, 0.047155316919088364, 0.006725584156811237, -0.060239046812057495, -0.003915448673069477, -0.008812300860881805, -0.038352858275175095, -0.016920585185289383, -0.0017415774054825306, 0.00021879056293983012, -0.01799706742167473, -0.039556652307510376, 0.0014996648533269763, 0.017787881195545197, -0.0399656742811203, -0.05177346244454384, -0.04077468812465668, -0.0035478067584335804, -0.011276700533926487, -0.04501739889383316, 0.0009855430107563734, -0.05851489305496216, 0.03290223330259323, -0.01484961062669754, 0.023032493889331818, -0.02665264904499054, 0.009692874737083912, 0.06847057491540909, 0.02198610082268715, 0.02811049111187458, 0.03652412071824074, 0.027531467378139496, -0.04728679358959198, -0.035815734416246414, -0.04440036416053772, 0.03469085693359375, -0.0026558255776762962, 0.